    <h1 property="name" id="wb-cont">Labour Program</h1>
    <p>The Labour Program promotes safe, healthy, fair and inclusive work conditions and cooperative workplace relations. The Labour Program is a federal institution that is part of Employment and Social Development Canada.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>
<div class="row">
